# CSS Typography

Typography controls the appearance of text.

## Font Family

```css
body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}
```

## Font Size

```css
p {
    font-size: 18px;
}
```

## Font Weight

```css
h1 {
    font-weight: bold;
}
```

## Text Alignment

```css
h1 {
    text-align: center;
}
```

## Line Height

```css
p {
    line-height: 1.8;
}
```

## Text Transform

```css
h1 {
    text-transform: uppercase;
}
```

## Real-World Example

Good typography improves readability and user experience.

## Summary

Typography plays a major role in professional web design.
